In all code: Use tab, NEVER spaces
Javascript, uses _ in names.
In HTML, uses _ in names.
In Python, uses _ in names.
Only open lines after different functions. Otherwise no blank lines.
Keep lines short and otherwise use enter to keep in tact.
In the repository: use a folder for all the data, a folder for all the scripts and a folder for the images. 
HTML and .md-files will directly be placed in the repository without subfolder.
In the folder for scripts, make a distinction external and own files.
Use only one-line comments in the script itself.
Datamap is the main visualisation, others are connected to the datamap scripts.
Do everything in English.
